title: Cats
description:
Seven incredible Cats!
You must just pat The Cats.
That's all!
The Cat nice purrs and vibrates...
You will get totally hooked on it.
At the end of a pleasant surprise...
Open all The Cats.
Two secret cats.

-= How to use =-
- Pat vibro cat.
- Enjoy the vibrations and purring.
- Open new Cats.

-= Features =-
- Live imitation of purring cat. 
- Sync with sound vibration.
- Seven funny Cats.
- Increase the volume during prolonged stroking.
- Reduce the volume in the absence of strokes.
- Funny cat animation.
- Hand-drawn graphics.
- Best for relax session.
- Universal love and happiness from vibrating cat
